Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.85,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.72,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.33,0:00:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.30,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.75,0:00:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.55,0:00:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.99,0:00:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.03,0:01:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.57,0:01:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.78,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.18,0:01:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.65,0:01:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.05,0:01:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!妳去拜託管理員\N叫她跟我約會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.36,0:02:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.53,0:02:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.66,0:02:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是大學生了\N想約會我自己會去約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不敢約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.20,0:02:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要知道,我也是有自尊心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.17,0:02:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,管理員很開心的答應了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.71,0:02:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少騙我了,我去拒絕她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.88,0:02:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約會這種事\N怎麼可以拜託別人出面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.55,0:02:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要再雞婆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶好像來\N拜託妳做很奇怪的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了我奶奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待這個星期日的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.89,0:03:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.69,0:03:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也很期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.40,0:03:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#35追蹤大作戰!\N瞄準響子和五代的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.38,0:03:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠了,不用送了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.12,0:03:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個,要照這個計劃進行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.75,0:03:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.73,0:03:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行程表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開…開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.91,0:03:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,奶奶,我們出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.91,0:04:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,能不能挽著手一起走?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,這樣太失禮了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶那種人不用理她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.01,0:04:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間已經完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.87,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,我們還沒談完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.27,0:05:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.04,0:05:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,不要走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.57,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我奶奶喜歡這種電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,我能了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代\N你們怎麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我想問你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生,拜託一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請安靜一點,好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,實在太令人震驚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.40,0:06:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒出聲叫你的話\N你根本不會察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.61,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你真是大膽\N一把就偷抓我的東西吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.95,0:06:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣,這是我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們安靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,爆米花請還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要吃?\N我可以分一點給你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來正好看的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人看到最後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.82,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.75,0:06:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.66,0:08:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.07,0:08:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.94,0:08:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按下這個按鈕就會前進喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,按下這個按鈕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑得好純真喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經擺出聖誕樹了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.42,0:09:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像太快了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.02,0:09:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太\N大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳又在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.63,0:10:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說偶爾也該\N買個東西給賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥和管理員?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.08,0:10:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪\N為什麼你們兩個人會在一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.25,0:10:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,這些錢拿去買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直待在這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我們先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.54,0:10:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太,那我們先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.12,0:10:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不覺得怪怪的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.19,0:11:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一之瀨太太\N居然沒有取笑我們耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.63,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了,而且時間也剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我們被跟蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧,她不可能那麼閒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.34,0:11:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,五代,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你想太多了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們出來吃飯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇啊,居然來這裡吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.86,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好稀奇喔\N你們居然兩個人一起出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,老闆經常請我吃飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.24,0:12:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這家是我很熟的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.13,0:13:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,真的好氣派喔\N居然在預約席用餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他們是出來約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得這會是巧合嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.94,0:13:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我覺得\N老闆應該不會這麼壞心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.54,0:13:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,是約會啊\N五代也蠻厲害的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,不是,是同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是奶奶和管理員同情他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們要不要出去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.57,0:13:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午三點鐘,古典咖啡店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.90,0:14:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你會不會口渴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.10,0:14:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.04,0:14:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.71,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生,請到那邊坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我們在找人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.86,0:14:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要我用麥克風幫你找?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.13,0:14:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳回去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了,快追!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的甩掉他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.36,0:17:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收您一千圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找您六百圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,快來買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.19,0:18:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是本公司引以為傲的新酒\N很好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往這裡\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.43,0:18:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,我好累喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.90,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊,快來買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.94,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是本公司引以為傲的新酒\N很好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,往這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.79,0:18:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是本公司引以為傲的新酒\N很好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.03,0:18:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太,這是我們的新酒\N要不要嚐嚐看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也好,我來試喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,謝謝兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,我累死了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.87,0:18:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就回去了,再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿杯果汁給小朋友喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代他們的事怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,有四谷跟著他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.06,0:19:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.76,0:19:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何?\N您府上都喝什麼酒呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家?我家都經常喝葉櫻酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純米酒也很不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很順口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太,您真是內行人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.23,0:20:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷他們好像沒有再追來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.03,0:21:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳今天陪我出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.43,0:21:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,真的好開心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.64,0:21:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.08,0:21:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在玩遊戲一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.28,0:21:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多…該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.81,0:21:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.91,0:22:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?沒有跡象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.01,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N我一直跟在後面偷偷監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.74,0:22:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了電影院\N卻一付很無聊的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.41,0:22:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且一直在看玩具\N沒有什麼交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.72,0:22:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在餐廳的氣氛也很尷尬\N他們馬上就離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.79,0:22:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,他們還在街上跑來跑去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.32,0:22:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來時間真的多到\N閒得無聊的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.13,0:22:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明就要回鄉下了\N一定很擔心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.13,0:22:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的事情\N請包在我們身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.44,0:22:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.71,0:22:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.75,0:22:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.52,0:23:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶,怎麼了?\N無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.19,0:23:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我花了好多功夫\N想把你們送做堆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.33,0:23:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美\N我受託照顧別人的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基於責任\N我不能讓這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.61,0:23:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.24,0:24:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「突來的親吻風暴!\N朱美的失戀物語」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.41,0:24:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的港邊\N當汽笛聲消失在夜空中時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.08,0:24:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.22,0:24:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.79,0:24:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.68,0:24:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.35,0:24:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.96,0:24:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.23,0:24:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.03,0:24:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.93,0:25:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.07,0:25:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.11,0:25:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.09,0:25:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.39,0:25:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
